Notes for Reviewers
•	This system is intentionally non-adaptive.
•	It is not a general-purpose chatbot.
•	It is not a therapeutic or coaching system.
•	Features such as adaptive LLM responses and therapeutic guidance were explicitly scoped out and documented as such.
The focus of this capstone is interaction integrity, safety, and constraint-based control, not user engagement optimization.

